1. Display hidden files

ls -a

2. renameRename all *.txt files to *.htm

john@john-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UAR:~/Desktop/Home_Practice$ rename 's/\.txt$/.htm/' *.txt
john.txt not renamed: john.htm already exists
john@john-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UAR:~/Desktop/Home_Practice$ ls
